---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Careers
description: "Join Samaritan and help build the future of AI-powered biomarker intelligence. We're hiring across engineering, clinical research, and more."
permalink: /careers/
---

<section class="careers-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow eyebrow-left eyebrow-teal">Careers</p>
    <h1 class="reveal">Build the future of kidney care</h1>
    <p class="careers-hero-lead reveal reveal-delay-1">
      We're a small team in Bengaluru working on one of the biggest unsolved problems in critical care.
      If you want your work to directly impact patient outcomes, we'd love to hear from you.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="careers-values">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="careers-values-grid">
      <div class="careers-value-card reveal">
        <div class="careers-value-icon"><i class="ph-fill ph-heart-half" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
        <h4>Mission-driven</h4>
        <p>Every line of code, every sensor calibration, every clinical conversation is in service of detecting kidney injury earlier and saving lives.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="careers-value-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="careers-value-icon"><i class="ph-fill ph-puzzle-piece" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
        <h4>Full-stack problems</h4>
        <p>We build hardware, AI, and software together. You won't work in a silo â€” you'll see how your work connects to the entire system.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="careers-value-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="careers-value-icon"><i class="ph-fill ph-rocket-launch" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
        <h4>Early stage, high impact</h4>
        <p>We're pre-clinical and growing. Joining now means shaping the product, the culture, and the company from the ground up.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="careers-openings" id="openings">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="reveal">Open Positions</h2>
    <p class="section-description reveal reveal-delay-1">
      All roles are based in Bengaluru unless noted otherwise. We're flexible on hybrid arrangements.
    </p>
    <div class="careers-list">
      {% for job in careers %}
        {% if job.active %}
        <div class="career-card reveal">
          <div class="career-card-header">
            <div>
              <h3>{{ job.title }}</h3>
              <div class="career-card-meta">
                <span>{{ job.department }}</span>
                <span class="career-meta-sep">&middot;</span>
                <span>{{ job.location }}</span>
                <span class="career-meta-sep">&middot;</span>
                <span>{{ job.type }}</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}?subject=Application%3A%20{{ job.title | urlencode }}" class="button button-primary career-apply-btn">
              Apply
              <i class="ph-fill ph-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            </a>
          </div>
          <p class="career-card-description">{{ job.description }}</p>
          {% if job.requirements %}
          <ul class="career-card-requirements">
            {% for req in job.requirements %}
            <li><i class="ph-fill ph-check-circle" aria-hidden="true"></i> {{ req }}</li>
            {% endfor %}
          </ul>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>

    <div class="careers-general reveal">
      <p>Don't see a perfect fit? We're always open to hearing from exceptional people. Send us a note at <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}">{{ site.email }}</a> and tell us what you'd bring to Samaritan.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
